          <li><a href="#article7">Article 7 - Conditions for consent</a></li>
          <li><a href="#article8">Article 8 - Conditions applicable to child's consent in relation to information society services</a></li>
          <li><a href="#article9">Article 9 - Processing of special categories of personal data</a></li>
